title: Virginia Tech holds 2022 Athletic Director's Honors Celebration - VT hokiesports.com
content: Virginia Tech holds 2022 Athletic Director's Honors Celebration  VT hokiesports.com
description: Virginia Tech's athletics department hosted the Athletic Director's Honors Celebration on Monday, March 21. The annual event was held at The Inn at Virginia Tech and resumed to being in-person for the first time since 2019, due to COVID-19.
